Sang Yi</b> គឺច្រៀង និងរាំបានយ៉ាងល្អ។</p><figure class="article-content-embed youtube"><div style="width: 100%; position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.21%; height: 0px;"><iframe allowfullscreen="" title="Lee Sang Yi" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" frameborder="0" width="781" height="439" src="./angkor1_files/0pblw38eciQ.html" style="position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 100%; height: 100%;"></iframe></div><figcaption class="article-content-caption"><i class="fal fa-video"></i> <span>Lee Sang Yi</span></figcaption></figure><p><b>៥. Lee Do Hyun</b></p><p><b>Lee Do Hyun</b> បង្ហាញខ្លួនលើកញ្ចក់ទូរទស្សន៍ដំបូង នៅឆ្នាំ
