និងកីឡាបែប​កាយសម្ព័ន្ធផងដែរ។</p><figure class="article-content-embed youtube"><div style="width: 100%; position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.21%; height: 0px;"><iframe allowfullscreen="" title="Lee Do Hyun" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" frameborder="0" width="781" height="439" src="./angkor1_files/JrsFJZpSEs8.html" style="position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 100%; height: 100%;"></iframe></div><figcaption class="article-content-caption"><i class="fal fa-video"></i> <span>Lee Do Hyun</span></figcaption></figure><p><b>៦. Hwang In Yeop</b></p><p>ប្រុសស្អាត<b> Hwang In Yeop </b>បានចាប់ផ្ដើមជាមួយ <b>Lee Do
