In Yeop</b> គឺសមត្ថភាពច្រៀង ដោយទទួលបានការលើកសរសើរជាហូរហែបន្ទាប់ពីច្រៀង ក្នុង​រឿង
<b>True Beauty</b>៕</p><figure class="article-content-embed youtube"><div style="width: 100%; position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.21%; height: 0px;"><iframe allowfullscreen="" title="Hwang In Yeop" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" frameborder="0" width="781" height="439" src="./angkor1_files/9LjxxZSYw0I.html" style="position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 100%; height: 100%;"></iframe></div><figcaption class="article-content-caption"><i class="fal fa-video"></i> <span>Hwang In Yeop</span></figcaption></figure><p><b>ប្រភព ៖ Soompi</b></p><div class="article-celebrities"></div><div class="article-tags"></div><div class="article-share"><i class="fal fa-share-nodes fa-xl"></i><div class="article-share-fallback "><div class="article-share-btn"><i class="fab fa-facebook fa-2x fa-fw" style="color: rgb(66, 103, 178);"></i></div><div class="article-share-btn"><i class="fab fa-facebook-messenger fa-2x fa-fw" style="color: rgb(0, 106, 255);"></i></div><div class="article-share-btn"><i class="fab fa-telegram fa-2x fa-fw" style="color: rgb(0, 136, 204);"></i></div><div class="article-share-btn"><i class="fab fa-twitter fa-2x fa-fw" style="color: rgb(0, 172, 238);"></i></div><div class="article-share-btn"><i class="fab fa-whatsapp fa-2x fa-fw" style="color: rgb(79, 206, 93);"></i></div><div class="article-share-btn"><i class="fab fa-viber fa-2x fa-fw" style="color: rgb(102, 92, 172);"></i></div><div class="article-share-btn"><i class="fab fa-linkedin fa-2x fa-fw" style="color: rgb(14, 118, 168);"></i></div></div></div></div></article><div class="grid-article-side"><div class="d-none-tablet" style="text-align: center;"><div id="gax-inpage-async-"></div></div><div class="article-related"><a class="article-related-writer" href="https://www.khmerload.com/writer/337"><img alt="Keo Rong" loading="lazy" width="60" height="60" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" src="./angkor1_files/12f918ba1c269fe13005b383463a5a85" style="color: transparent;"><div class="article-related-name">K.R </div></a><h2>អត្ថបទទាក់ទង</h2><div class="article-list small"><article class="article-list-item"><a class="article-list-item-thumbnail" href="https://www.khmerload.com/article/203747"><img alt="//s9.kh1.co/0c/0c3b0a74303ebad80d922af7155cfa3dad1c3b6e.jpg" loading="lazy" width="250" height="130" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" src="./angkor1_files/0c3b0a74303ebad80d922af7155cfa3dad1c3b6e.jpg" style="color: transparent;"></a><div class="article-list-item-detail"><a href="https://www.khmerload.com/article/203747"><h3 class="article-list-item-detail-title">បើមានសញ្ញា ៧យ៉ាងនេះ បានន័យថាគាត់គិតចង់រៀបការជាមួយអ្នកហើយ</h3></a><div class="article-list-item-detail-datetime"><i class="fal fa-calendar-days"></i>&nbsp;២៤-ឧសភា-២០២៤&nbsp;</div><div class="article-list-item-detail-datetime"><i class="fal fa-clock"></i>&nbsp;៤ល្ងាច&nbsp;·&nbsp;២ ឆ្នាំមុន</div></div></article><article class="article-list-item"><a class="article-list-item-thumbnail" href="https://www.khmerload.com/article/196551"><img alt="//s9.kh1.co/8f/8f08e1fec693bfe0e4efe043e56bc85b8597a469.jpeg" loading="lazy" width="250" height="130" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" src="./angkor1_files/8f08e1fec693bfe0e4efe043e56bc85b8597a469.jpg" style="color: transparent;"></a><div class="article-list-item-detail"><a href="https://www.khmerload.com/article/196551"><h3 class="article-list-item-detail-title">ហៅតារានិករទាំងនេះ Date ដូចហៅគោមើលកុន</h3></a><div class="article-list-item-detail-datetime"><i class="fal fa-calendar-days"></i>&nbsp;២៤-មីនា-២០២៣&nbsp;</div><div class="article-list-item-detail-datetime"><i class="fal fa-clock"></i>&nbsp;២ល្ងាច&nbsp;·&nbsp;៣ ឆ្នាំមុន</div></div></article><article class="article-list-item"><a class="article-list-item-thumbnail" href="https://www.khmerload.com/article/196550"><img alt="//s9.kh1.co/ee/ee2e7c73615abb0637d0dd2cf7502b04301edc0d.jpeg" loading="lazy" width="250" height="130" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" src="./angkor1_files/ee2e7c73615ab